manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

playstore_details.title: MINT Browser - Secure & Fast
playstore_details.description:
**Now with Tor support & fingerprint scanning!**

Perfect incognito & privacy? Compact? And speedy? We've got you covered. 
This is MINT Browser® (Patent Number US10706175B2) - the most powerful web browser that's straight to the point. 


SPEEDY 💨
Slick design means faster loading. MINT Browser's architecture is designed to be speedy like a lightweight browser, but not lightweight in features.

TOR SUPPORT 🌰
Not only does MINT Browser support proxying through Tor - it also patches the infamous WebRTC bug that leaks sensitive information when Tor is used. Did you know this bug is still unpatched in many other browsers?

INCOGNITO+ (Patent Pending) 🔒   (Patent Number 10706175)
In Incognito+, browsing data is private to your eyes only. Access Incognito+ by long clicking the hat button. Alternatively, you can use normal incognito by just clicking the hat button.

PRIVATE BOOKMARKS, HISTORY, NOTES ⭐ 
Bookmark your favorite incognito pages, keep track of your incognito history, and make private notes. Your Incognito+ bookmarks, history, and notes are encrypted.

FINGERPRINT SCANNING 🤞 
Access Incognito+ with secure fingerprint scanning. No need to type that password each time!

TAKE NOTES 📝 
Instead of having to constantly switch between apps to take notes, take notes and browse – all on the same screen.

WEATHER ❄️ 
See local weather conditions right on your homepage.
(Requires location access)

SPEED DIAL 🔘 
Pin your favorite pages to the homepage for quick access.

AND MORE ✔️
Premium:
SYNC ☁️ 
Sync your bookmarks & notes across your devices, even ones made in Incognito+!

AD-BLOCKER 🛡 
Browse more comfortably, without annoying ads.
(It also blocks trackers automatically!)
